About the job
Decathlon wants to move people through the wonders of sport.

The Finance Team is engaged in transforming itself and contributing to the transformation of the company, creating fulfilling professional projects for our teams, improving efficiency through mutualization, automation and digitalization, assure the security of the activity and the reliability of information, and support our teams to make data based decisions.

To accelerate the transformation path, the Financial Center of Excellence in Singapore is looking for Accounting Specialists - Process Referent.

Function: Specialized accounting

Process: Retail accounting processes

Scope: Regional

Responsibilities


Actively participate in the setup of a Finance Center of Excellence in Singapore to mutualise the accounting processes;
Perform the activities of the process according to the established standards and assure the reliability of the information;
Provide support and communicate with the Country Relays of our partners about the accounting processes, ensuring the fulfillment of the Service Level Agreement;
To be recognised as a referent, pro-actively contribute to the continuous improvement of the process in terms of efficiency and automation;
Contribute to the improvement of the competence level of the teams, through defining standard procedures;
Integrate the international referents network and contribute to the process development and standardisation


Requirements


Passionate about sports and active;
Bachelor in Finance-related discipline, with previous work experience of 3-5 years;
Good knowledge of Accounting and Finance Tools i.e. ERP;
Team Player, able to work in autonomy as well as with others;
Proactive, prioritise and take decisions;
LEAN methodology and thinking;
Sense of organization, attention to detail and ability to deliver according to the standards;
Good communication skills;
Good English level (mandatory), other languages knowledge is valued;
Project Management skills are valued;


Benefits


Variable monthly performance bonus (up to 10%)
Be a shareholder, with exclusive annual option to invest in Decathlon shares. 
Opportunity to work in a international, sporty environment
Staff discount across all Decathlon brands
Internal and external training available


By applying, you consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal data in accordance with our Privacy Policy (https://www.decathlon.sg/s/privacy-policy).

